project_descr: The POAG in the Red Sea State project aims at creating institutional, social and economic environment conducive for poverty reduction in the Red Sea State of Sudan through innovative interventions and constructive partnership.

outputs.output_descr: Strengthen the capacity of the State administration at all levels in designing and implementing pro-poor strategies and ensuring sound development resources management.
